pg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据透露，<a href="/artists/isley-brothers">艾斯利兄弟</a>将就艾斯利兄弟乐队名称的权利向法庭提起诉讼。</p><p>鲁道夫·艾斯利和罗纳德·艾斯利两兄弟自今年早些时候以来一直就乐队名称的所有权问题陷入法律纠纷。据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/isley-brothers-court-battle-over-band-name-legal-rights-1235399882/"><em>Billboard</em></a>报道，在 8 月 23 日星期三做出的裁决中，托马斯·M·德金法官拒绝驳回鲁道夫对罗纳德的诉讼。</p><p>在诉讼中，鲁道夫指控他的兄弟罗纳德不当试图以“艾斯利兄弟”的名字注册个人商标。鲁道夫认为他们应该平等地拥有一半的权利。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CtP78whvjgG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999