年组建的乐队的标志性名称。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-isley-brothers-headed-to-court-over-band-name-trademark-3488711">艾斯利兄弟 (The Isley Brothers) 因乐队名称商标问题而告上法庭的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
